NOTE on data and content:

The plant data files in `src/data/plants/` and the rendered web content are
derived from public-domain and open-access sources (EMA, Kommission E, ESCOP,
WHO Monographs, PFAF, Wikipedia, Henriette's Herbal, Madaus 1938, Künzle 1911,
Hildegard von Bingen, etc.) and the author's synthesis thereof.

These plant-data files and rendered texts are released under
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC-BY-SA 4.0).
See: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Plant images are sourced from Wikimedia Commons under their respective
CC licenses. Attribution metadata (`image.license`, `image.author`,
`image.source_url`) is stored in each plant JSON. Downstream users must
preserve attribution per the source license.
